Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 09 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Vessels/Ureter' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Abdominal aorta' radio button is enabled
And 'Common iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'External iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Internal iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Inferior vena cava' radio button is enabled
And 'Common iliac vein' radio button is enabled
And 'External iliac vein' radio button is enabled
And 'Ureter' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Abdominal aorta' radio button
Then 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Abdominal aorta'radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled
When I enter "1" in the 'Maximum diameter' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter "9999" in the 'Maximum diameter' input field
Then the value is accepted

When I select 'Common iliac artery' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Right' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Left' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Elongation' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled

When I enter "1" in the 'Maximum diameter' input field
Then the value is accepted
When I enter "9999" in the 'Maximum diameter' input field
Then the value is accepted

